You have the right and may cancel your paid subscription at any time. But you must be aware and consent that some of your personal information will be transferred to the third-party payment vender (such as Apple Pay, Google Pay, Stripe, etc.) you used to make the payment. The transferred information is for the purpose of ensuring an accurate cancellation. The personal information to be collected and transferred will include, but not limited to, days of your account registration, active hours of your account, the in-app virtual merchandise you have purchased, usage of your purchased in-app virtual merchandise, value of your purchased in-app virtual merchandise, etc.
